Title: Series: The childhood of Christ
Description: The Virgin seen riding a donkey side-saddle with the infant Christ in her lap; Joseph leading the way on foot, his hand resting on the neck of the donkey; a small golden statue seen on a tree, to right (the sun?); in the background, to left, men harvesting and Herod's soldiers in horseback; plate 8; on full sheet; after Maarten de Vos. Engraving
Bibliographic references: Hollstein / Dutch and Flemish etchings, engravings and woodcuts c.1450-1700 (269) (Maarten de Vos)
